1. *Opa* je bio stariji muškarac koji je ispunjavao ulice osmehom. (Grandpa was an older man who filled the streets with smiles.) 
2. *Opi* su se deca igrala u parku. (The kids were playing in the park.)
3. Ona je imala *opu* veo. (She had an old veil.)
4. Ona ga je primila sa *opom*. (She received it with gratitude.)
5. On je bio uzbuđen za svoju *opu*. (He was excited for his grandpa.)